Package org.eclipse.persistence.services.websphere

Class MBeanWebSphereRuntimeServices

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.persistence.services.RuntimeServices
      • org.eclipse.persistence.services.websphere.WebSphereRuntimeServices
        • org.eclipse.persistence.services.websphere.MBeanWebSphereRuntimeServices
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MBeanRuntimeServicesMBean, MBeanWebSphereRuntimeServicesMBean
    public class MBeanWebSphereRuntimeServices
extends WebSphereRuntimeServices
implements MBeanWebSphereRuntimeServicesMBean

    Purpose: Provide a dynamic interface into the EclipseLink Session.

    Description: This class is meant to provide a framework for gaining access to configuration of the EclipseLink Session during runtime. It will provide the basis for development of a JMX service and possibly other frameworks.

    Since:
    EclipseLink 2.1.1
